rop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color:=
 #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; borde=
r-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc=
;"> a surprising statistic</a>:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">AI is also expensive, both to deve=
lop and to run. Estimates show the costs of using large language models to =
answer a question can be as much as $14 per query, compared with $6 via a h=
uman lawyer, according to Lewis Z. Liu, founder and CEO at Eigen. That=E2=
=80=99s because of the extensive cloud computing costs associated with deal=
ing with complex financial documents.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Umm! My understanding is that a fairly junior =
lawyer=C2=A0at a big law firm=C2=A0can <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombe=
rgbusiness.com/click/31662572.286417/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYWJham91cm5hbC5jb20vbm=
V3cy9hcnRpY2xlL25lYXJseS0xMDAwLWFuLWhvdXItaXMtcmF0ZS1mb3Itc2Vjb25kLXllYXItY=
XNzb2NpYXRlLWF0LXRoZXNlLWJpZ2xhdy1maXJtcw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBd9961bd6=
" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D=
"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px=
; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-colo=
r: #ccc;">bill $1,000 per hour</a>. Six dollars would buy about 22 seconds =
of her time. You could probably get a lawyer to answer a question like =E2=
=80=9Cis it raining outside your office right now?=E2=80=9D for less than=
=C2=A0you=E2=80=99d pay a large language model=C2=A0(and get a more accurat=
e answer!), but if your question <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusi=
ness.com/click/31662572.286417/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9u=
L2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjItMDctMTgvZWxvbi13YW50cy10by1maWdodC10aGUtYm90cz9jbXBpZD1=
CQkQwNjAxMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldH=
RlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzA2MDEmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a=
319a23cB6794a272" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"=
_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-b=
ottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid;=
 background-color: #ccc;"> is more like</a> =E2=80=9Cif the target of my me=
rger agreement won=E2=80=99t give me all the information I have requested a=
bout bots, what provisions of the merger agreement might allow me to walk a=
way from the deal, and what are my odds of success,=E2=80=9D ChatGPT is def=
initely going to be cheaper. Will it be better? Probably not! But surely no=
 one in the history of the world has ever before said =E2=80=9Cthe nice thi=
ng about lawyers is that they will happily answer questions for $6 a pop.=
=E2=80=9D=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">That statistic is from <a href=3D"https://link=
.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31662572.286417/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZ=
XJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2ZlYXR1cmVzLzIwMjMtMDUtMzEvanBtb3JnYW4tcy1wdXNoLWludG8tZmlu=
YW5jZS1haS1oYXMtd2FsbC1zdHJlZXQtcnVzaGluZy10by1jYXRjaC11cD9jbXBpZD1CQkQwNjA=
xMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWlsJnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG=
1fdGVybT0yMzA2MDEmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cC=
95005314" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" =
style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-wi=
dth: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; backgro=
und-color: #ccc;">  a Bloomberg story</a> about how financial firms are usi=
ng artificial intelligence tools to do, well, a little of everything:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The AI revolution is unfolding on Wall Street =
as wider interest grows in the evolving technology and its likely impact on=
 business. At the most enthusiastic banks, about 40% of all open job roles =
are for AI-related hires such as data engineers and quants, as well as ethi=
cs and governance roles, according to new data from consultancy Evident. =
=E2=80=A6</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The potential prize for businesses is that eve=
ryday tasks will be handled more efficiently and effectively while complex =
analysis and risk modeling are made easier and faster. That=E2=80=99s parti=
cularly tempting in banking, where reams of data underpin increasingly comp=
lex investment decisions, despite uncertainties about AI=E2=80=99s eventual=
 capabilities and concerns about how to regulate it.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The process has already begun, according to la=
wyers advising lenders on technology and regulatory issues. Banks are using=
 AI =E2=80=9Cto come up with more tailored hedging solutions through instru=
ments like interest-rate swaps and equity derivatives, enabling them to off=
er better pricing to clients,=E2=80=9D said Steven Burrows, a director at F=
ieldfisher LLP and a former derivatives trader.</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">No idea what that means but it sounds fun! And=
:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Wells Fargo is using large languag=
e models to help determine what information clients must report to regulato=
rs and how they can improve their business processes. =C2=A0=E2=80=9CIt tak=
es away some of the repetitive grunt work and at the same time we are faste=
r on compliance,=E2=80=9D said Chintan Mehta, the firm=E2=80=99s chief info=
rmation officer and head of digital technology and innovation. The bank has=
 also built a chatbot-based customer assistant using Google Cloud=E2=80=99s=
 conversational AI platform, Dialogflow.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Do you think that Wells Fargo=E2=80=99s custom=
er chatbot pushes customers to <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusine=
ss.com/click/31662572.286417/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2=
FydGljbGVzLzIwMTYtMDktMDkvd2VsbHMtZmFyZ28tb3BlbmVkLWEtY291cGxlLW1pbGxpb24tZ=
mFrZS1hY2NvdW50cz9jbXBpZD1CQkQwNjAxMjNfTU9ORVlTVFVGRiZ1dG1fbWVkaXVtPWVtYWls=
JnV0bV9zb3VyY2U9bmV3c2xldHRlciZ1dG1fdGVybT0yMzA2MDEmdXRtX2NhbXBhaWduPW1vbmV=
5c3R1ZmY/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB2cf8bf25" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscop=
e=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration:=
 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> open more accounts to =
meet its quotas</a>? Do you think that its regulatory-reporting chatbot the=
n reports it to regulators? Soon Wells Fargo may be able to generate and ne=
gotiate <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31662572.2=
86417/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY29uc3VtZXJmaW5hbmNlLmdvdi9hYm91dC11cy9uZXdzcm9vbS9jZ=
nBiLW9yZGVycy13ZWxscy1mYXJnby10by1wYXktMzctYmlsbGlvbi1mb3Itd2lkZXNwcmVhZC1t=
aXNtYW5hZ2VtZW50LW9mLWF1dG8tbG9hbnMtbW9ydGdhZ2VzLWFuZC1kZXBvc2l0LWFjY291bnR=
zLw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB153d0fbe" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"=
itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none=
 !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border=
-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">billion-dollar regulatory se=
ttlements</a> without any human involvement at all.=C2=A0</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The downside =E2=80=94=C2=A0besides paying $14=
 per question I guess =E2=80=94=C2=A0is that large language models are know=
n to sometimes be confident and wrong:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Bankers have a fiduciary duty not =
to trade on unreliable information. That=E2=80=99s an issue as use of AI ex=
pands, according to Anne Beaumont, partner at Friedman Kaplan Seiler Adelma=
n &amp; Robbins LLP in New York. =E2=80=9CHow do you demonstrate to investo=
rs and regulators that you=E2=80=99ve done your duty when you=E2=80=99ve us=
ed an output without really knowing what the inputs are?=E2=80=9D she said.=
</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">And another Bloomberg story, this one <a href=
=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31662572.286417/aHR0cHM6L=
y93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDUtMzEvaGVkZ2UtZnVuZHMt=
YXJlLWRlcGxveWluZy1jaGF0Z3B0LXRvLWhhbmRsZS1hbGwtdGhlLWdydW50LXdvcms_Y21waWQ=
9QkJEMDYwMTIzX01PTkVZU1RVRkYmdXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbCZ1dG1fc291cmNlPW5ld3NsZX=
R0ZXImdXRtX3Rlcm09MjMwNjAxJnV0bV9jYW1wYWlnbj1tb25leXN0dWZm/607f07ceef4b8524=
a319a23cB73335905" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D=
"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-=
bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid=
; background-color: #ccc;"> about hedge funds using AI to automate tasks</a=
>, adds:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The technology isn=E2=80=99t perfe=
ct, however. ChatGPT has been known to make up facts and spit out different=
 responses to the same prompt, and is only trained on data up to late 2021.=
 Meanwhile, in an industry where trade secrets are anxiously guarded, many =
are still hesitant about relying on external software.=C2=A0</p></blockquot=
e>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Isn=E2=80=99t this sort of exciting? The wides=
pread use of relatively early-stage AI will introduce=C2=A0<em>new ways of =
making mistakes=C2=A0</em>into finance. Right now there are some classic wa=
ys of making mistakes in finance, and they periodically lead to consequence=
s ranging from funny embarrassment through multimillion-dollar trading loss=
 up to systemic financial crises. Many of the most classic mistakes have th=
e broad shape of =E2=80=9Coverly confident generalizing from limited histor=
ical data,=E2=80=9D=C2=A0though some are, like, <a href=3D"https://link.mai=
l.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31662572.286417/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnL=
mNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDItMTcvY2l0aS1jYW4tdC1oYXZlLWl0cy05MDAt=
bWlsbGlvbi1iYWNrP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA2MDEyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWw=
mdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDYwMSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZX=
lzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB53779a4b" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscop=
e=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration:=
 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> hitting the wrong butt=
on</a>. But there are only so many ways to go wrong, and they are all sort =
of intuitive.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">But now there are new ways! Weird ways! Oh sur=
e an AI can probably make overly confident generalizations from limited his=
torical data, but perhaps there is room for novelty. Now some banker is goi=
ng to type into a chat bot =E2=80=9Cour client wants to hedge the risk of t=
he Turkish election,=E2=80=9D and the chat bot will be like =E2=80=9Cshe sh=
ould sell some Dogecoin call options and use the proceeds to buy a lot of n=
ickel futures,=E2=80=9D and the banker will be like =E2=80=9Cweird okay wha=
tever.=E2=80=9D And that trade will go wrong in surprising ways,=C2=A0=C2=
=A0the client will sue,=C2=A0the client and the banker and the chat bot wil=
l all come to court,=C2=A0the judge will ask the chat bot =E2=80=9Cwell why=
 would this trade hedge anything,=E2=80=9D and the chat bot will shrug its =
little imaginary shoulders and be like =E2=80=9Cbro why are you asking me I=
=E2=80=99m a chat bot.=E2=80=9D Or it will say =E2=80=9Cactually the Dogeco=
in/nickel spread was ex ante=C2=A0an excellent proxy for Turkish political =
risk because=E2=80=9D and then emit=C2=A0a series of ones and zeros and emo=
jis and high-pitched noises that you and I and the judge can=E2=80=99t unde=
rstand but that make perfect sense to the chat bot. New ways to be wrong! I=
t will make life more exciting for financial columnists, for a bit, before =
we are all replaced by the chat bots.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Elsewhere in lawyers and AI and confident wron=
gness, <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/31662572.28=
6417/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuY25uLmNvbS8yMDIzLzA1LzI3L2J1c2luZXNzL2NoYXQtZ3B0LWF2aW=
FuY2EtbWF0YS1sYXd5ZXJzL2luZGV4Lmh0bWw/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB2275e265" it=
emprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"col=
or: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; bo=
rder-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #=
ccc;">here is a story</a> about a lawyer=C2=A0suing Avianca SA in a New Yor=
k federal court who had ChatGPT write a brief for him. ChatGPT made up some=
 fake case citations, which he included in his brief. The other side couldn=
=E2=80=99t find the cited cases, so the court asked the lawyer to provide c=
opies of the decisions, so he asked ChatGPT for them, and ChatGPT made them=
 up and he submitted them. Bad bad stuff!=C2=A0 Astonishing new ways to be =
wrong!=C2=A0Here is the judge=E2=80=99s <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomb=
ergbusiness.com/click/31662572.286417/aHR0cHM6Ly9zdG9yYWdlLmNvdXJ0bGlzdGVuZ=
